{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858222748,"sessionID":"ses_2869a6fcdffesb4bjHj9DaiIpE","part":{"id":"prt_d7965e72b001SC3OveC0zg7Zxp","messageID":"msg_d7965d8f000163CeWhY4Rcx3g8","sessionID":"ses_2869a6fcdffesb4bjHj9DaiIpE","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_1a8e902bf3e84a96ae2671a8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-015/README.md","content":"# AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API\n\n**Module:** pkg/picod  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M\n\n## Summary\n\nImplement PicoD command execution API for the pkg/picod module.\n\n## Status\n\n- [x] Scaffold directory structure\n- [ ] Implement PicoD command execution API\n- [ ] Add unit tests\n- [ ] Add integration tests\n\n## Notes\n\nSee `notes/` directory for implementation notes and decisions.\n\n## Source Files\n\nSee `src/` directory for source code changes.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-015/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-015/README.md","time":{"start":1775858222727,"end":1775858222747}}}}
